response.overview: While vacationing in sunny California a young couple realize they are in the land of Powers, Ed Powers. They wrote old Ed a letter months back about the possiblity of Heather making a video with Rick, her husband. So the circumstances came full circle. This couple have had sex exclusively with each other, now for the first time another male is allowed to enter this happy picture and lucky Ed was chosen, did he step in it or what?  We go Deep Inside to find out why and how this all came about. You'll feel the excitement when another man touches wife and the actual joy that is felt by the husband as he watches and videotapes the action...  Slender and so exciting is Rebecca as she experiences her very first time on camera, you'll almost be able to hear her heart racing with that excitement... Pulse pounding... Humping... Spoozing heat all pours out when you go Deep Inside Dirty Debutantes...
response.title: Deep Inside Dirty Debutantes 2
